OL,3,C'Unimaginable tragedy': Family's
OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FViewers may find some of the details
OL,8,Fin this report upsetting.
OL,10,FA Co Antrim man who admitted murdering
OL,11,Fand dumping a father-of-two in a
OL,12,Freservoir in Carrickfergus in March
OL,13,F2022 has been sentenced to 21 years.
OL,15,FThe court heard how 34-year-old
OL,16,FMichael Campbell of Maghaberry prison
OL,17,Fstabbed, kicked and punched Roy
OL,18,FReynolds in a savage attack before
OL,19,Fbundling the 54-year-old into a boot
OL,20,Fand then disposing his naked body.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/13
