OL,3,C'Unimaginable tragedy': Family's
OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHis co-accused, 70-year-old Robert
OL,8,FMervyn Fulton of Brickhill park in
OL,9,FNewtonabbey, was given two years and
OL,10,Ffour months but has already spent time
OL,11,Fin custody so was released on license
OL,12,Fafter pleading guilty to helping
OL,13,Ftransport the body in his car.
OL,15,FMr Reynolds sustained more than 100
OL,16,Finjuries in what the Judge described
OL,17,Fas "brutal in the extremes, relentless
OL,18,Fand merciless. This was a savage
OL,19,Fmurder".
