OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Reynolds' family
OL,8,Fsaid: "We, Roy's family, find
OL,9,Fourselves in the midst of an
OL,10,Funimaginable tragedy. Our beloved Roy
OL,11,FReynolds, affectionately known as
OL,12,FFobby, was taken from us far too soon.
OL,14,F"As we grapple with grief, we want to
OL,15,Fexpress our heartfelt gratitude to
OL,16,Feveryone who has stood by our side
OL,17,Fduring this harrowing time.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/13
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
