OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"First and foremost, we extend our
OL,8,Fdeepest appreciation to the members of
OL,9,Four family and public who bravely
OL,10,Fstepped forward and shared their
OL,11,Faccounts with the authorities. Your
OL,12,Fcourage in reliving painful memories
OL,13,Fhas not gone unnoticed. Together, we
OL,14,Fseek justice for Roy, and your
OL,15,Funwavering support strengthens our
OL,16,Fresolve."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/13
