OL,7,FThe family added: "To the public,
OL,8,Fwhose compassion and empathy have
OL,9,Ftouched our hearts, we say thank you.
OL,10,FYour kind words, gestures, and
OL,11,Fpresence have provided solace when
OL,12,Fwords fail us. Your solidarity reminds
OL,13,Fus that we are not alone in this dark
OL,14,Fhour.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/13
