OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"We reserve a special place of honour
OL,8,Ffor the individual who reported the
OL,9,Fincident to the police. Your swift
OL,10,Faction ensured that Roy's case
OL,11,Freceived immediate attention. Your
OL,12,Fvigilance matters, and we are forever
OL,13,Fgrateful for your role in bringing
OL,14,Fthis tragedy to light.
OL,16,F"To the member of the public who
OL,17,Fdiscovered Roy and promptly alerted
OL,18,Fthe authorities, we express our
OL,19,Fheartfelt appreciation.
