OL,7,F"Additionally, we extend our gratitude
OL,8,Fto the Police Service of Northern
OL,9,FIreland. Your tireless efforts in
OL,10,Finvestigating this heartbreaking
OL,11,Fincident are deeply appreciated. We
OL,12,Ftrust in your commitment to justice
OL,13,Fand accountability.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/13
