OL,3,C'Unimaginable tragedy': Family's
OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"Fobby was more than a name; he was a
OL,8,Fcherished brother, father, and
OL,9,Fgrandfather. His twin sister, Maggie,
OL,10,Fshares our grief, as do his brother
OL,11,FPhillip and sisters Samantha, Joanne
OL,12,Fand Donna. Roy's legacy lives on
OL,13,Fthrough his daughters, Natasha and
OL,14,FLisa, and his three precious
OL,15,Fgrandchildren: Charlie, Freya, and
OL,16,FAyda.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G8/13
