OL,3,C'Unimaginable tragedy': Family's
OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"In this time of sorrow, we kindly
OL,8,Frequest privacy for our family. We
OL,9,Fneed space to mourn, to remember, and
OL,10,Fto find strength in each other. Please
OL,11,Frespect our need for solitude as we
OL,12,Fnavigate this painful journey."
OL,14,FPPS Senior Public Prosecutor Mairead
OL,15,FLavery said "Campbell subjected Mr
OL,16,FReynolds to a ferociously violent and
OL,17,Fsenseless attack, inflicting a
OL,18,Fhorrific catalogue of more than 100
OL,19,Findividual injuries".
