OL,3,C'Unimaginable tragedy': Family's
OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe Senior Public Prosecutor added:
OL,8,F"After the murder he called Fulton who
OL,9,Fagreed to drive him to the reservoir
OL,10,Fwhere Campbell attempted to conceal Mr
OL,11,FReynolds' body by attaching his
OL,12,Fremains to a cement block and putting
OL,13,Fhis body in the water. Had his remains
OL,14,Fnot been discovered hours later by a
OL,15,Fmember of the public, these callous
OL,16,Factions could have robbed his family
OL,17,Fof a burial."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G10/13
