OL,4,Canguish as man jailed for 'merciless'
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"The prosecution team in the PPS
OL,8,FSerious Crime Unit worked closely with
OL,9,Fthe Police Service of Northern
OL,10,FIreland, who had carried out a
OL,11,Fthorough investigation, to bring
OL,12,FCampbell and his co-accused before the
OL,13,Fcourt and build a strong case against
OL,14,Fboth defendants resulting in guilty
OL,15,Fpleas.
